Package us.ullberg.startpunkt.graphql

Class BookmarkGraphQLResource

java.lang.Object
us.ullberg.startpunkt.graphql.BookmarkGraphQLResource
@GraphQLApi @ApplicationScoped public class BookmarkGraphQLResource extends Object
GraphQL API resource for bookmarks. Provides queries for retrieving bookmarks grouped by their group property.
